        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Tales From Across The Table - Episode4: Chip and a Chair]]></title>
            <itunes:title><![CDATA[Tales From Across The Table - Episode4: Chip and a Chair]]></itunes:title>

            <description><![CDATA[
        <p>"Chip and a Chair" follows Rico—the eagle, storyteller and analyzer—as he relives a defining moment from a massive No‑Limit Hold'em tournament at the legendary Commerce Casino. The episode blends survival, psychology, and the craft of hand reading through a cinematic retelling of what happens when you're reduced to a single chip in a room full of killers.</p>
        <p>From one chip to a playable stack, Rico breaks down hand reading and table image manipulation. A masterclass in short-stack strategy and opponent profiling.</p>
      ]]></description>

